<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>AtomicLab</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body>

<div style="background-color: #fafafa;">
    <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; font-family: 'Roboto', helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 800px; padding-bottom: 50px; padding-left: 2px; padding-right: 2px; position: relative; width: 100%;">
        <div style="background-color: #4772b2; padding: 30px 0px 20px 0px; position: relative; text-align: center;">
            <img src="http://limbs.azurewebsites.net/content/img/logoatomicmail.png" style="max-width: 200px; min-width: 100px; position: relative; text-align: center; width: 50%;">
        </div>
        <div style="margin: 0px auto; max-width: 475px; position: relative; width: 94%;">
            <!-- Caja 1 -->
            <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #dddddd; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 26px; margin: 30px 0px; padding: 10px 20px; position: relative; width: 100%;">
                <p style="color: #263238; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 30px; text-align: center;">¡Hola @(Model.OrderAmbassador.AmbassadorName)!</p>
                <p>Gracias por imprimir y ensamblar la solicitud de @(Model.OrderRequestor.ResponsableName). Ahora queda hacerle llegar su mano y la dirección es: </p>
                <p>@(Model.OrderRequestor.Address), @(Model.OrderRequestor.City), @(Model.OrderRequestor.Country)</p>
                <p>
                    <img src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=@(Model.OrderRequestor.Address),@(Model.OrderRequestor.City),@(Model.OrderRequestor.Country)&zoom=16&size=300x300&maptype=roadmap%20&markers=color:blue%7Clabel:S%7C@(Model.OrderRequestor.Address),@(Model.OrderRequestor.City),@(Model.OrderRequestor.Country)" />
                </p>

    
                <p>Si estas en Argentina, te proveemos de forma gratuita el envío por correo.</p>
                
                <p style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; text-align: center;">
                    <a href="http://limbs.azurewebsites.net/orders/details/@(Model.Id)" style="background: #4772b2; border-radius: 17px; color: white; padding: 8px 15px; text-decoration: none;">Ir al sitio</a>
                </p>
                <p>¡Saludos!</p>
                <p>El equipo de Atomic Lab.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #232323; color: #bbbbbb; padding: 40px; text-align: center;">
            <p>Atomic Lab es una iniciativa que busca inventar las mejores soluciones para ayudar a las personas.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="http://atomiclab.org/" target="_blank" style="color: #bbbbbb;">Limbs, Atomic Lab © 2017 - AtomicLab.org</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>